================================================================================
                            PROJECT COMPONENTS
================================================================================

This license applies to all components of the ClaimHeart project:

FRONTEND (Next.js Application)
  - React components and pages
  - TypeScript code and types
  - UI/UX designs and layouts
  - State management (Zustand)
  - Styling and themes

BACKEND (FastAPI Application)
  - Python API endpoints
  - OCR processing engine (EasyOCR integration)
  - Medical data parser
  - Database models and schemas
  - Authentication and security

DOCUMENTATION
  - README files
  - API documentation
  - Setup guides
  - Code comments

CONFIGURATION FILES
  - Docker configurations
  - Environment templates
  - Build scripts

