MEDICAL DISCLAIMER:
This software is designed for medical claims processing and document analysis.
It is NOT intended to:
  - Provide medical advice
  - Replace professional medical judgment
  - Be used as a sole diagnostic tool
  - Make clinical decisions without human oversight

Users are responsible for:
  - Ensuring compliance with healthcare regulations (HIPAA, GDPR, etc.)
  - Validating all extracted medical data
  - Maintaining patient privacy and data security
  - Following local laws and regulations

